(90, 197, 'JA Teline IV for T3', 'ja-teline-iv-now-on-t3-framework', '<p>Following up our previous Joomla template upgrades <strong><a href="http://www.joomlart.com/updates/joomla-templates/responsive-joomla-template-for-news-ja-nex-now-on-t3v3-framework" title="">JA Nex</a></strong> and <strong><a href="http://www.joomlart.com/updates/joomla-templates/responsive-joomla-template-for-social-ja-social-now-on-t3v3-framework" title="Joomla template JA Social in T3 Framework">JA Social</a></strong>, our popular Responsive Joomla template for News - <strong><a href="http://www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-teline-iv" title="More info about Joomla template JA Teline IV">JA Teline IV</a></strong> has been upgraded to be compatible with the latest version of <strong><a href="http://t3-framework.og" title="T3 Framework" style="text-decoration:none" target="_blank">T3 Framework</a></strong> for Joomla 2.5 and Joomla 3.</p>\r\n\r\n', '\r\n<p>JA Teline IV version 1.0.0 is available with the following great extensions:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ja-checklist">\r\n<li>JA News featured</li>\r\n<li>JA Newsticker</li>\r\n<li>JA Twitter</li>\r\n<li>JA Newspro</li>\r\n<li>JA Facebook Likebox</li>\r\n<li>JA Disqus Debate Echo plugin</li>\r\n<li>JA Popup Plugin</li>\r\n<li>JA Thumbnail Plugin</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\n<p>More details on this update can be read at its changelog and don’t forget to back-up your site before proceeding to any of the upgrading process.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="alert alert-info ja-msg-box">\r\n<div class="ja-msg-box-ct clearfix" align="left">\r\n<p><strong>JA Teline IV for T3 Framework </p></strong>\r\n<ul class="ja-ctlist ctlist-menu">\r\n<li><a href="http://joomla-templates.joomlart.com/ja_teline_iv_t3" style="text-decoration:none" title=" JA Teline IV for T3 Framework Demo">Demo for Joomla 2.5 & Joomla 3</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.joomlart.com/forums/downloads.php?do=cat&id=510" style="text-decoration:none" title=" JA Teline IV for T3 Framework Download">Dow