(91, 198, 'T3 Framework 2.0.2 released', 't3-framework-v2-0-2-released', '<p>We have upgraded the powerful Joomla template framework - T3 Framework 2.0.2 to the latest version of Joomla 3.2.1 and Joomla 2.5.17.</p> \r\n<p>In case you are new to T3, here are some key features of this Joomla framework:</p>\r\n', '\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fully Responsive</li>\r\n<li>HTML5, Bootstrap 3 and LESS</li>\r\n<li>Comes with 2 starter themes</li>\r\n<li>Flat design</li>\r\n<li>Supports Megamenu and Off-canvas</li>\r\n<li>Flexible layout system</li>\r\n<li>Joomla 2.5 and Joomla 3 native</li>\r\n<li>Supports Real Time Theme Customization</li>\r\n<li>Supports Font Awesome 3 & 4</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In this update, we have included numerous bug fixes with two improvements. Those are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Add condition to load old javascript only in Joomla 2.5.x</li>\r\n<li> Add gutter width on thememagic for T3 B3 Blank template</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>More details can be read at its changelog below and please ALWAYS back up your site before proceeding to the update process.</p>\r\n<div class="ja-msg-box">\r\n<div class="ja-msg-box-ct clearfix" align="left">\r\n<ul class="ja-ctlist ctlist-menu">\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="http://update.joomlart.com/#compare/T3/2.0.2/2.0.1" title="Compare Joomla template framework - T3 Framework version 2.0.2">Compare</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="https://github.com/t3framework/t3/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md" title="Joomla template framework - T3 Framework version 2.0.2 Changelog">Changelog</a>\r\n</li>\r\n\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="http://demo.t3-framework.org/joomla25/" title="Joomla template framework - T3 Framework version 2.0.2 - Demo for Joomla 2.5">Demo Joomla 2.5</a>\r\n<a href="http://demo.t3-framework.org/joomla30/" title="Joomla template framework - T3 Framework version 2.0.2 - Demo for Joomla 3.2">Demo Joomla 3.2</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="https://github.com/t3framework/t3/releases/tag/v2.0.2" title="Download Joomla template framework - T3 Framework version 2.0.2 from Github">Download from Github</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.joomlart.com/forums/downloads.php?do=cat&id=473" title="Joomla template framework - T3 Framework version 2.0.2 - Demo for Joomla 3.2">Download from Joomlart</a>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Upgrade steps</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="ja-checklist">\r\n<li>View the comparison between versions at <a href="http://update.joomlart.com/" title="Joomlart version update and comparison" target="_blank">JoomlArt Version Updates</a> and replace the affected files, if you have not customized the affected files.</li>\r\n<li><strong>RECOMMENDED</strong> : Use <a href="/joomla/extensions/ja-extensions-manager">JA Extension Manager</a> Component for upgrade. Watch <strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NCufzI-Z6cM&amp;list=PL4BjMzuBkvR_WDwn30cfWF9W9_PUDjiZa">video</a></strong> for how to upgrade using JAEM.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Any issue related to the above can be discussed at T3 Framework forums.</p>', 1, 80, '2013-11-15 08:26:09', 42, '', '2014-01-23 08:54:23', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2013-11-15 08:26:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"images\\/joomlart\\/stories\\/demo-s2.jpg","float_intro":"right","image_intro_alt":"T3 Framework 2.0.2 released","image_intro_caption":"T3 Framework 2.0.2 released","image_fulltext":"images\\/joomlart\\/stories\\/demo-s2.jpg","float_fulltext":"right","image_fulltext_alt":"LESS","image_fulltext_caption":"LESS"}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","s