(154, 378, 'JA Bookshop', 'ja-bookshop', '<p>Responsive Joomla template for Ecommerce</p>\r\n ', '\r\n<p>for Joomla 3.2 and Joomla 2.5 – JA Bookshop is a supreme template for online bookstores or any type of e-commerce site. It is built on the robust T3 Framework with Bootstrap 3, supports RTL language layout, fully responsive and brings in an pleasing blogging experience with EasyBlog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>JA Bookshop will definitely boost up your e-stores with the vigorous shopping cart component – Mijoshop. This feature-rich component is compatible with thousand of Opencart extensions and supports numerous payment and shipping gateways which would assure you an ideal solution for your online business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Available in 5 color schemes and 8 bonus pages, JA Bookshop is a perfect choice for an elegant and multi-functional e-store website.</p>', 1, 83, '2014-01-06 09:22:31', 42, '', '2014-01-25 08:59:36', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-01-06 09:22:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"images\\/joomlart\\/portfolio\\/ja_bookshop.jpg","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"JA Bookshop","image_intro_caption":"JA Bookshop","image_fulltext":"images\\/joomlart\\/portfolio\\/ja_bookshop.jpg","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"JA Bookshop","image_fulltext_caption":"JA Bookshop"}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"",