(159, 383, 'JA Fixel', 'ja-fixel', '<p>Responsive Joomla 3 & Joomla 2.5 template</p>\r\n', ' \r\n<p>JA Fixel - responsive template for Joomla 2.5 & Joomla 3 version. It supports EasyBlog (Joomla blogging component) and JoomShopping (Shopping cart component). The template also supports RTL language layouts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shines through with its innovative flat design and minimalistic trend: bold colorblocking and bright typo, together with JoomShopping and EasyBlog component, JA Fixel is a complete business eCommerce solution for your Joomla site. Comes in 8 color schemes and 8 bonus pages, supporting 5 different grid styles and various content types. JA Fixel is ready-set-go for your business innovation to go all out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fully responsive, JA Fixel looks stunning on just any screen size. JA Fixel fits best for business portfolio, personal blog, digital media or cartography galleries with a touch of eCommerce solution. It\'s definitely a must-have Joomla template for this summer.</p>', 1, 83, '2014-01-06 09:35:53', 42, '', '2014-01-25 08:55:30', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-01-06 09:35:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"images\\/joomlart\\/portfolio\\/ja_fixel.jpg","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"JA Fixel","image_intro_caption":"JA Fixel","image_fulltext":"images\\/joomlart\\/portfolio\\/ja_fixel.jpg","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"JA Fixel","image_fulltext_caption":"JA Fixel"}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":""